data.title: Wonderful assortment of fine art - both 3D and 2D
data.text: The Taylor Kinzel Gallery has been one of our favorite art galleries in Roswell GA for many years.  The assortment of art, both 2D (paintings) and 3D sculptures is far ranging both is style and pricing.  It is always fun to just wander through, with the real possibility of finding a real treasure.  The setting is among quaint old Roswell center with many other shops and resturants.
